name: 35ft & 40ft MacDon 75D Header Pack
description:
This is my first public mod conversion release. I hope you all enjoy it!

Credits to Julian11 FS17, Smeby FS19, and thank you to Pleasant View Farms for working with me in blender.

Thanks to Happy View Farms, Farmer Taz, and Pleasant View Farms for helping me test them.

Check out their channels on Youtube for some great FS22 content!

This will receive updates as I continue to work on it. Make sure to follow this page so you can receive notification when they get updated. I plan to bring the 45 ft head back in a future update.

UPDATE 1.1 - Added the correct width and adjust the price of the 35ft in the store menu.
